l</category><category>joint compound</category><description>Compare mesh screens vs paper for drywall sanding. Learn which to use, what grit, tools, and dust control for crisp joints and a clean finish.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="mesh-vs-paper-smarter-drywall-sanding-choices"&gt;Mesh vs Paper: Smarter drywall sanding choices&lt;/h2&gt;
