ridges, and get a pro finish with Lucas Moreno’s step‑by‑step guide.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="figure-eight-pole-sander-drywall-technique"&gt;Figure-Eight Pole Sander Drywall Technique&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first time I learned the figure‑eight, it was 6 a.m., coffee in a paint-stained thermos, and a living room taped up like a crime scene. The house belonged to a neighbor who’d done an earnest DIY skim coat. The seams were proud, ridges crisp as a credit card. I’d already spent too many nights fighting walls with the wrong motion: straight up and down, back and forth, carving tracks with a pole head that liked to dig in at the end of each stroke. If you’ve ever wrestled a pole sander drywall on a long seam, you know that end-of-stroke gouge—the one that laughs at you when the primer hits it.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/12.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Set Up Dustless Drywall Sanding With Shop Vac</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 21 Nov 2025 16:22:15 +0000</pubDate><category>Drywall Sanding</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-220</category><category>dust control</category><description>Learn how to set up dustless drywall sanding with a shop vac for cleaner, faster results. Pro-tested gear, step-by-step setup, and practical sanding tips.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-drywall-sanding-with-a-shop-vac-setup"&gt;Dustless drywall sanding with a shop vac setup&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’ve walked into more living rooms covered in drywall dust than I care to admit. It’s in the couch seams, the AC returns, your morning coffee—everywhere. You think you’ll “just scuff the patches,” then the sun hits the air like a stage light and there it is: a snow globe from floor to ceiling. I’ve been there—rushed deadlines, fresh paint booked for tomorrow, and a client who can’t breathe if dust drifts beyond the plastic. That’s why I preach dust control like it’s a religion, especially when we’re sanding drywall. With a proper setup for dustless drywall sanding using a shop vac, you don’t just keep the room livable—you work faster, see your surface better, and stop clogging your lungs and your vacuum.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/27.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/>